Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 今天的飯菜也好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這些怪話是跟誰學的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}BigBird!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里安也注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}掉地上就會被牠吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}深感慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}BigBird也是 好好做隻鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}亂吃東西會搞壞肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 爸爸的頭髮睡亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}認真完成每一個動作 不出現失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目前進展還順利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接下來是NHK杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也見到了 年輕人的勢頭真的很猛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是說南野嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}並不只是他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我說的是肩負著體操界未來的新人們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們需要做的事情並沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不斷積累 不斷進步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且所有項目的動作都必須做到精確
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}否則就失去了意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}需要更加地集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瀧 Joe他們在談什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}NHK杯的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}NHK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}N…叛逃忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}肚子的袋子裡有袋鼠!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}NHK杯 是個超級大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}超級?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}體操界超級厲害的大賽有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}選拔一下的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最後剩下些厲害的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}厲害的選手中再選拔厲害的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說這大賽超級厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}害怕了吧 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}超級厲害的關原之戰在等待Joe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}關原之戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下次不是決鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又可以看到Joe在大舞台上表演了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你為什麼這麼想看我表演體操
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你來我們家的時候就在說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍法·跪拜術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要奪走Joe的體操
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼要做到那個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以前就知道我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為Joe很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在江戶村有名?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我幫助Joe只有一個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下是荒垣家的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}武士 武士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不退役
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咚!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「咚」那一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼要那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為小玲看起來不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒有不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他們一直都那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要告訴爸爸他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「咚」也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要接近我的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不聽我的話 我就和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}絕交?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城太郎 差不多到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲最近怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 她幫了很多忙 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她現在在上小學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前段時間剛升上四年級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是嗎 她是個好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和知世很像 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的 我現在能在這練習都是多虧了玲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我聽我女兒說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像最近在班裡挺流行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還可以拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我每天都在拍照發給女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過她也不回復
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小步 我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝妳輔導我的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不客氣 小玲這麼聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲說要和我絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}步閣下 絕交是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯…一輩子不見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為何?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是赤壁之戰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}注意到的時候已經不妙了 一片火海的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赤…壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有些時候就是搞不懂風向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}緊張感滿滿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我上學去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爸爸路上也小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}路上注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那孩子今天不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他說什麼紅色峭壁來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好 抓緊時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}馬上就響鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:09:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看吧 叮咚叮咚 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下 這邊這位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下來這裡調查事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下 什麼事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這裡沒有小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}該接受調查的是你好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先把你頭上的東西摘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無禮之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你才是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天的比賽我來了個帽子戲法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}厲害 你是羅納爾多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}厲害 亨利啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想看看我表演博格坎普停球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 傳一下通知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}傳一下 傳一下 我也轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 荒垣 這次家長參觀日武士會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還是不會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}武士不會參加授課參觀!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}停一停吧 男生們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲家的武士可忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下次再輸可能就真的要退役了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里安 你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被看穿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不愧是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是媽媽的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳母親的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}媽媽 他叫里安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是從江戶村跟來的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在住在我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下里安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲的母親是一位知名演員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還不只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}媽媽平時也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她什麼都很會做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}料理的手藝也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總是為爸爸加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總是面帶笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親和小玲很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我差遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也要像媽媽一樣努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自從遇到了小玲 在下每天都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們收留了我 陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我幸福極了 十分感激
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在正是在下報恩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}該去奶奶的店裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都說了 客人坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有你不練習嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}練習很快就結束了 很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再說這點事一般人都會做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里安 辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剛才回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說是作業寫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟糕 里安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}家長參觀日 好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下 上次是什麼時候來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}記不得了 不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.17,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我失憶了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}家長參觀日?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}懂吧 就是媽媽會認真準備的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告訴她那樣反而會顯得輕浮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}結果就挨打的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}麻里店長 辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從哪裡找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在垃圾桶裡發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲不小心丟掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下去送給她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里安 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟糕 炒烏冬套裝沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們去買
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}套裝 等…什麼套裝?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現成的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下 小步 我們一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}家長參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也去過 去過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奶奶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳家武士沒來 奶奶來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奶奶不像武士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那武士呢 武士今天不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:14:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奶奶 今天大家都在說武士 很吵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}平常不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奶奶有工作 結果還讓妳來參加…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她是個善良的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過她在意的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一有什麼事情 就會責怪自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她爸爸是那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怎麼樣都會受到關注
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然她丟掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說明我去也不過是給她添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然在下看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有做出行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}麻里閣下 在下有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 爸爸關好門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不聽我的話 我就和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里安 該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下今天不去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯? 你有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Joe好好練習
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全力參加關原之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下一個 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我媽媽來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你家人真是認真!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小和家媽媽也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有誰家的沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像有個厲害的傢伙來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外國人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是誰的哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大帥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是誰的哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}班裡有外國人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荒垣哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}做出來的人 舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個人一直在給你加油 不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是說荒垣同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就荒垣同學來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}317餘1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正確
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好棒! 鼓掌!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲! 好棒!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了好了 大家靜一靜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下一題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好 小玲!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下一題也會 提問她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 別怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 小玲 小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里安 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 在下和他們成為好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(756.95,657.00)\blur2\fsp0.4\fs32\fnSitka Small\b1)\i1}Rachel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼要叫她 小玲?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里安和她是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下是保護小玲的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍者!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 大家都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以和他們做朋…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你個蠢忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼和他們玩得這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Rachel聽著像好萊塢演員一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我沒反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一群人一直這麼叫 我能開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有你為什麼在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒說過家長參觀日的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}搞不懂 你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有那件衣服是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不是忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總是聚在一起 有什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喊著武士 把別人當傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們和我爸爸說過話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們知道他每天都練習到晚上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒什麼不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爸爸真的是世界第一的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和爸爸比 你們就是一群足輕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:34.65,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}註：足輕是日本平安時代到江戶時期的一種步兵。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跪拜術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為小玲沒有笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為妳在學校看起來不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下希望妳能露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無論何時何地 我都想幫助妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都怪里安 我成了發火的角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想說的話全都說出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真苦惱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 妳能原諒我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天去學校我該怎麼表現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真的覺得對不起嗎
