Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說好了 只有里安可以叫我小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 得去買牛奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交給在下
